snippet.title: Five Day Detective Trailer (New Version)
snippet.description:
This is the higher-quality trailer for our upcoming 'walk and click' adventure, Five Day Detective. The full game is scheduled for 2025, but the demo is available here:
Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2582400/Five_Day_Detective/ 
itchio:
https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io/five-day-detective
Music is Lipstick Lies and Batting Lashes by Bryan Teoh
